    "Salehi et al. (2020) implemented a CNN to classify and diagnose AD at early stages using MRI images.",
    "It is implemented with TensorFlow on a system with graphics Intel HD 6000 1536 MB and 8GB RAM, reaching 99% accuracy.",
    "It combines two image data sources to increase the quantity of images, resulting in models performance improvement.",
    "The restriction is that the moderate dementia class is not included.",
    "Ajagbe et al. (2021) presented a multi-classification of AD with CNN, VGG16, and VGG19."
